      About this item

      • No Heat Retention: Ideal for storing cold beverages and keeping them cold for a few hours only, Please note that this bottle does not have heat retention capability and is not suitable to retain temperature of hot beverages
      • Leak Proof: The bottle has a wide cap sealed with a flip top and is completely leak proof when laid on its side or even shaken.
      • Food safe and Odourless: Made with food grade plastic the bottle is 100% non toxic and safe to store beverages while retaining flavour and being odourless
      • Handy and Durable : Made of BPA free food safe plastic this water bottle is built to last with a curvy shape that ensures a better grip and a handy wrist strap helps carry it with ease and also hang if necessary
      • Easy To Clean- The bottle is easy to clean with a mild detergent and bottle brush
      • Color:Assorted, Material: BPA Free Food grade plastic

          What is in the box?

          • Product Description

          "Sportigo Plastic Water Bottle: Your Hydration Partner for an Active Lifestyle"

          Discover unparalleled convenience with the Sportigo Plastic Water Bottle. Designed to be lightweight and compact, these bottles are perfect for everyday use. They seamlessly blend style and quality, offering an array of assorted colors with impressive durability. Made from 100% food-grade plastic, these bottles ensure both safety and hygiene for your hydration needs.

          BPA FREE Plastic Material

          Experience safety and convenience with our high-quality, BPA-free plastic bottle. Prioritizing your well-being, this bottle gives you a hygienic experience every time you use it. Its sleek, ergonomic design and compact size ensure effortless portability, allowing you to take it with you wherever you go.

          Easy to carry loop!

          Simplify your life with the built-in easy-to-carry loop on our bottles. This feature allows you to transport your bottle with utmost ease. Whether you're heading to the gym, office, or a stroll, the convenient loop ensures a comfortable and secure grip and gives you smooth handling.

          Easy to open and close!

          Experience unmatched convenience with our flip-top lid bottle. Effortlessly open and close the lid for hassle-free sips on the go. Now quench your thirst without any fuss or spills.

          Meet your ultimate hydration companion - the Sportigo Plastic Water Bottle. This versatile buddy is ready to accompany you to the gym, work, and beyond. Stay refreshed wherever you go with this bud by your side.

          Get a perfect match for your style and needs with a variety of colors and capacities to choose from.
